description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Cooter purrs with a rating of 87, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 174, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 8 for East, Box for South, and Nine Lives for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90872-78492-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [174 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
